# Check that UCI time control arguments work properly
uci
position startpos
go depth 12 nodes 0 wtime 2500 btime 2500 winc 100 binc 100 movestogo 20 wait
# With a total time budget of 2500, per turn time should be between 100 and 999ms
expect time [1-9][0-9][0-9] exceeded
expect bestmove [a-h][1-8][a-h][1-8]
